 828: **Implementation:**
 829: 
 830: ```python
 831: def run_py(code: Optional[str] = None,
 832:            file: Optional[str] = None,
 833:            auto: Optional[str] = None) -> Dict[str, Any]:
 834:     # Auto-detect file vs code
 835:     if auto is not None:
 836:         if "/" in auto or auto.endswith(".py"):
 837:             file = auto
 838:         else:
 839:             code = auto
