 47: ‚îÇ  ‚îú‚îÄ Find symbol ‚Üí mcp__syntropy__serena_find_symbol
 48: ‚îÇ  ‚îî‚îÄ Symbol usage ‚Üí mcp__syntropy__serena_find_referencing_symbols
 49: ‚îÇ
