572: ### ce init-project
573: 
574: **Purpose**: Initialize CE Framework in target project
575: 
576: **Usage**:
577: ```bash
578: cd tools
579: uv run ce init-project ~/projects/target-app
580: 
581: # With flags
582: uv run ce init-project ~/projects/app --dry-run
583: uv run ce init-project ~/projects/app --phase extract
584: uv run ce init-project ~/projects/app --blend-only
585: ```
586: 
587: **When to use**:
588: - Setting up CE framework in new project
589: - Upgrading existing CE installation
590: - Re-initializing after major changes
591: 
592: **Output**: 4-phase pipeline (extract ‚Üí blend ‚Üí initialize ‚Üí verify)
593: 
594: **See**: [ce-init-project-usage.md](ce-init-project-usage.md) for comprehensive guide
595: 
596: ---
597: 
598: ### ce blend
599: 
600: **Purpose**: Merge CE framework files with target project customizations
601: 
602: **Usage**:
603: ```bash
604: cd tools
605: uv run ce blend --all
606: uv run ce blend --claude-md --memories
607: uv run ce blend --all --target-dir ~/projects/app
608: ```
609: 
610: **When to use**:
611: - After updating framework files (memories, examples)
612: - Re-merging user customizations
613: - Upgrading framework content
614: 
615: **Domains**: CLAUDE.md, memories, examples, settings, commands, PRPs
616: 
617: **See**: [ce-blend-usage.md](ce-blend-usage.md) for comprehensive guide
618: 
619: ---
