621: ### ce update-context
622: 
623: **Purpose**: Sync PRPs with codebase implementation state
624: 
625: **Usage**:
626: ```bash
627: cd tools
628: uv run ce update-context
629: uv run ce update-context --prp PRPs/executed/PRP-34.1.1-core-blending-framework.md
630: ```
631: 
632: **When to use**:
633: - After completing PRP implementation
634: - Weekly system hygiene
635: - Detecting pattern drift
