637: **Auto-features**:
638: - Rebuilds repomix packages if framework files changed
639: - Detects drift violations
640: - Updates YAML headers
641: 
642: **See**: `.claude/commands/update-context.md`
643: 
644: ---
645: 
646: ### ce validate
647: 
648: **Purpose**: Validate project structure and framework files
649: 
650: **Usage**:
651: ```bash
652: cd tools
653: uv run ce validate --level all
654: uv run ce validate --level 4  # Pattern conformance
655: ```
656: 
657: **Levels**:
658: - L1: File structure
659: - L2: YAML headers
660: - L3: Content validation
661: - L4: Pattern conformance
662: 
663: **See**: `.serena/memories/l4-validation-usage.md`
664: 
665: ---
