667: ### ce vacuum
668: 
669: **Purpose**: Clean up temporary files and obsolete artifacts
670: 
671: **Usage**:
672: ```bash
673: cd tools
674: uv run ce vacuum                  # Dry-run (report only)
675: uv run ce vacuum --execute        # Delete temp files
676: uv run ce vacuum --auto           # Delete temp + obsolete
677: ```
678: 
679: **See**: `.claude/commands/vacuum.md`
680: 
681: ---
682: 
683: ### CE Command Patterns
684: 
685: **‚úÖ CORRECT**:
686: ```python
687: # Use ce commands for framework operations
688: Bash(command="cd tools && uv run ce blend --all")
689: Bash(command="cd tools && uv run ce init-project ~/projects/app")
690: ```
691: 
692: **‚ùå WRONG**:
693: ```python
